<h2 class='date-header'>Thursday, 1 February 2018</h2>
<div class='post hentry'>
<a name='655317140709574313'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title'>
<a href='http://www.lettersofnote.com/2018/02/letters-live-los-angeles.html'>LETTERS LIVE LOS ANGELES</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-author'>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content'>
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<iframe allowfullscreen="" class="YOUTUBE-iframe-video" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2WFD38j2F5A/0.jpg" frameborder="0" height="300" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2WFD38j2F5A?feature=player_embedded" width="520"></iframe></div>
<br />
Hello all,<br />
<br />
Do you live in or around L.A.? If so, you are duty-bound to attend <a href="https://www.axs.com/events/347820/letters-live-tickets?skin=acehotel">Letters Live on February 26th</a> at the historic Ace Hotel Theatre in Downtown Los Angeles for what will be our first public show in the U.S. It promises to be an incredible evening: talented performers bringing to life letters from throughout the ages in one of the city's most gorgeous venues. Truly an event like no other. Better still, all profits from tickets sales will go to charity, split equally between <a href="http://826la.org/">826LA</a>, who support students with creative and expository writing skills, and <a href="https://www.womenforwomen.org.uk/">Women for Women International</a>, a non-profit humanitarian organisation providing practical and moral support to female survivors of war.<br />
<br />
<b>To grab some tickets for this special event, please <a href="https://www.axs.com/events/347820/letters-live-tickets?skin=acehotel">visit this link</a>.&nbsp;</b><br />
<br />
To learn more about Letters Live, head over to the website where you can find info on <a href="http://letterslive.com/events/">previous/forthcoming events</a> and watch some&nbsp;<a href="http://letterslive.com/letters/?show=all">footage of readings</a>.<br />
<br />
I shall be back soon with more news, fresh letters, a revamped website, and various other things I'm straining to keep under my hat.<br />
<br />
In the meantime, I shall hopefully see you in L.A.!<br />
<br />
All my love,<br />
Shaun<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
